IPV4 has 4 class
Class A = 0-127    default subnent - >  255.0.0.0
class B = 128 - 191  default subnent - >  255.255.0.0
Class C = 192 - 223  Default Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0
class D = 224 - 239  multicat - vidio striming and etc 
class E = 240 - 255  reserved for researches 

note : the class D and E didnt hade any subnenting 

